│ iteration and simplifying the remaining loop, exit phi nodes get values from peeled iterations instead of the correct values from the remaining loop.                                                          │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ The specific issue in test `pr114879.ll` is that `%retval.2.lcssa.ph` gets `%retval.2.peel` (which is `undef`/`null`) instead of `@GlobIntONE`. This happens because:                                          │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ 1. The loop is peeled, creating `%retval.2.peel` in the peeled iteration                                                                                                                                       │
